    <name>Blinded</name>
    <slug>blinded</slug>
    <content>&lt;h3 id="blinded"&gt;&lt;a id="blinded-blinded"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a id="blinded"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Blinded&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class="small-text"&gt;&lt;a href="home"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="conditions"&gt;Conditions&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; Blinded&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;blinded&lt;/strong&gt; creature cannot see and:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="square"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;checks based on sight fail,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;attacks against it have advantage,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;its attacks have disadvantage,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p class="small-text"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Source: Player&amp;#x2019;s Handbook, p. 290&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
  </page>
  <page id="6bad69c9-e5a3-5ce1-92d4-880a16d0510a" sort="1" parent="2e5061d8-871b-53bb-b7c7-80ed942b1a30">
